              80% is a bit high, but this is very much a case of abandon ware. Emkorial can literally not buy from the manufacturer that which he is proxying. It's not like he's proxying Innistrad cards. He is proxying cards that have been out of production and only available on the secondary market by mail order for not inconsiderable expense.<br /><br />Don't hate. Don't create bad metaphors. This is closer to ScummVM than hacked xbox360.

              

              
              
